Package: debian-lsp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Language Server Protocol implementation for Debian control files
 Debian LSP provides a language-server for editing Debian control and related
 files, offering field completion, diagnostics, and quickfixes. It builds the
 `debian-lsp` Rust binary and installs it to `/usr/bin`.
